      Your email is verified. You’ll get the free Income ETF Starter Guide when the next release goes out — we’ll
      never sell your address, and you can unsubscribe any time from future mailings.
    </p>
    <a class="mt-8 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900" href="/etfs"
      >Explore the ETF directory →</a
    >
  </section>
</Base>
